# Keep these out of the image — they're either not needed at runtime,
# or (in the sqlite case) we specifically don't want a stale/dev copy of
# the database baked into the image itself; it should only ever exist in
# the mounted volume, created fresh by the app on first save.
.git
.gitignore
README.md
data/networkkb.sqlite
data/networkkb.sqlite-journal
